WEBVTT

00:09.303 --> 00:10.787
Hello?

00:10.789 --> 00:13.056
LINDA:
In the kitchen.

00:13.974 --> 00:16.209
Something smells good.
What are you cooking?

00:16.210 --> 00:18.728
Duck.
Duck?

00:18.730 --> 00:20.730
Mm-hmm, duck.

00:20.732 --> 00:23.399
Do the boys like duck?

00:23.401 --> 00:25.902
The boys aren't home.
Mm.

00:25.904 --> 00:27.187
They're at a sleepover.

00:27.189 --> 00:28.822
Mm. Then I guess

00:28.824 --> 00:31.324
it's just you
and me and the duck.

00:31.326 --> 00:33.576
Yup.
That sounds delicious.

00:33.578 --> 00:34.894
(laughs)

00:34.896 --> 00:36.112
Hmm.

00:36.114 --> 00:38.698
You want to open
some wine for us?

00:38.700 --> 00:40.366
Mm-hmm, okay.

00:40.368 --> 00:43.002
(phone ringing)

00:43.004 --> 00:44.787
Sorry.

00:44.789 --> 00:46.756
Gormley?

00:46.758 --> 00:48.791
No.

00:48.793 --> 00:50.877
Marianne Romano.

00:50.879 --> 00:52.773
You are not going over
there to kill a spider.

00:52.798 --> 00:53.931
I know. I know.

00:53.932 --> 00:55.298
Hello.
MARIANNE: Danny?! Danny! Danny?!

00:55.300 --> 00:57.550
What is it?
MAN: Hang it up, you stupid bitch!

00:57.552 --> 00:58.918
Marianne, who is that?
MAN: You hear me.

00:58.920 --> 01:00.220
MARIANNE:
Danny, he's gone insane!

01:00.222 --> 01:01.387
Who's gone insane?

01:01.389 --> 01:03.389
What? Will you calm down?
MARIANNE: Danny! No!

01:03.391 --> 01:04.757
Hello?
(beep)

01:04.759 --> 01:07.560
Sounds like some guy's
over there beating on her.

01:07.562 --> 01:10.280
Yeah, or she just turned up
the volume on <i>Maury Povich.</i>

01:10.282 --> 01:11.764
You know I got to go.

01:11.766 --> 01:13.316
Hurry back, okay?

01:13.318 --> 01:15.985
I will. Mmm.

01:16.891 --> 01:20.891
